line_1: For these must be provided sundry Meats,
line_2: The Best for Some, for Others coarser Cates.

line_1: Artists must chuse his Pictures, Music, Meats:
line_2: Not for himself he sees, or hears, or eats;

line_1: That pamper'd Him with sav'ry Meats;
line_2: Thanks to her Book of choice Receipts,

line_1: Frank Carves very ill, yet will palm all the Meats:
line_2: He Eats more than Six; and Drinks more than he Eats.
